Date:	Mon Mar 12 15:03:18 PST 1984
From:	ucbopal:genji (Genji Schmeder)
Subject: misinformation in manual page
Index:	man/man2/send.2  4.2BSD  Fix

Description:
   Manual page prescribes a non-existent defined constant
   for the flags parameter:

      .PP
      The
      .I flags
      parameter may be set to SOF_OOB to send \*(lqout-of-band\*(rq
      data on sockets which support this notion (e.g. SOCK_STREAM).

Fix:
   Change SOF_OOB to MSG_OOB.
